# ğŸ“„ Chat with Multiple PDFs using Gemini

This project is a **Streamlit-based application** that enables users to **upload multiple PDF files** and interact with them using **Google's Gemini AI model**. The app extracts text from PDFs, processes it into vector embeddings using FAISS, and allows users to ask questions based on the content of the uploaded documents.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

âœ… **Upload multiple PDF files**
âœ… **Extract and split text for efficient processing**
âœ… **Convert text into embeddings using Google's Generative AI**
âœ… **Store and retrieve information using FAISS (Facebook AI Similarity Search)**
âœ… **Chat with your PDFs using a conversational AI model**
âœ… **Intuitive web interface built with Streamlit**

